            <div type="apparatus">
                <p>Text of Manganaro 1989</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>[-----] to Alb[---] Pompeius Marcellus, his patron, an excellent man, well deserving.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Manganaro speculatively restores the name as [-]Cornelius Albinianus Pompeius Marcellus, but this seems pure speculation, as does the claim that the missing dedicant in the first part of the text was 'certamente un Cornelius(?) Pompeius'.</p>
            </div>
